To run TransformerForBrasetCancer.jl and CUDATransformerForBreastCancer.jl download first the ndatasets:


https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/sabahesaraki/breast-ultrasound-images-dataset?resource=download

https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/orvile/bus-uclm-breast-ultrasound-dataset

Then extract them at the directory named "data/" at the folder that you run the code.

